reviewText: The unrated version is definitely the one to get.  I have seen both and the R rated one leaves you wanting to see more of the incredible beauties in the film.  The script is not bad for a "skin flick" and the acting is above average for this kind of feature.  The show is very much focused on the women who are much better than the "boy-toy" males.  The heroine comes out ahead in the end and good triumphs over evil.  I would have given the film a 4 1/2 star rating if possible. The sexy women and outfits deserve 5 stars.
